description: This file is a header file declaring interface functions for a String Array Object component in a C-based system, including creation, removal, object enrollment, and initialization functions.

methods.name: AnscCreateStringArrayComponent
methods.description: Creates a new String Array component with specified container, owner, and reserved handles.

methods.name: AnscStringArrayCOCreate
methods.description: Creates an instance of the String Array Object with specified context and ownership handles.

methods.name: AnscStringArrayCORemove
methods.description: Removes an existing instance of the String Array Object.

methods.name: AnscStringArrayCOEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls necessary objects for the String Array Object.

methods.name: AnscStringArrayCOInitialize
methods.description: Initializes the String Array Object instance.
